# Cursor Collaboration Rules

1)  Always confirm **monorepo** context; operate at workspace root. Use
    pnpm filters when running scripts.
2)  Never introduce Next.js to the backend; backend is **Express**.
3)  Any suggestion that adds Redis must keep `DISABLE_REDIS=true` path
    working.
4)  Keep changes minimal & reversible; prefer PRs with clear diffs and
    tests.
5)  When unsure, generate an **Audit Report** answering the inventory in
    this doc before changing code.

